3)\lim_{x \to \infty}\frac{x^2+1}{x^3}= \lim_{x \to \infty}\frac{1+\frac{1}{x^2}}{x}=\lim_{x \to \infty}(\frac{1}{x}+\frac{1}{x^3})= " 0 + 0"= 0
